<body>
<div class="work-item">
<img src="c610abf2-0c13-4b90-abd4-4db609b655ab.png" alt="Personal Blog and School Portfolio">
<div class="work-desc">
<h4>Personal Blog & School Portfolio</h4>
<p>This project showcases my journey as a student — featuring my reflections, favorite works, and creative outputs throughout the school year.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="work-item">
<img src="Screenshot 2025-10-08 at 5.15.22 PM.png" alt="Links and Images">
<div class="work-desc">
<h4>Links and Images</h4>
<p>A compilation of my favorite artists, media inspirations, and creative layouts inspired by music and design aesthetics.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="container contact">
<h3>Contact Me</h3>
<form class="contact-form" action="#" method="post">
<label for="name">Name:</label>
<input id="name" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Enter your name" required>

<label for="find">Where did you find me?</label>
<select id="find" name="find">
<option value="facebook">Facebook</option>
<option value="google">Google</option>
<option value="friends">Friends</option>
</select>

<label for="email">Email:</label>
<input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>

<label for="rating">Rate my portfolio (1-10):</label>
<input id="rating" name="rating" type="number" min="1" max="10" placeholder="10" required>

<label for="feedback">Feedback:</label>
<textarea id="feedback" name="feedback" rows="4" placeholder="Write your feedback here..."></textarea>

<button class="btn" type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
</section>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
<div class="container">
<p>© <span id="year"></span> Melcy Benasas — OB Montessori | ICT 9 Section</p>
</div>
</footer>

<script>
document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>
</body>
